| # | Requirement | Implementation |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Search input at the top | `<input type="search">` rendered before the list |
| 2 | Custom 300 ms debounce (no lodash) | `useDebounce` hook using `setTimeout` / `clearTimeout` inside `useEffect` |
